[Actions]
Active=planPitstop,simulatePitstop,updateStrategy
[Builtin]
planPitstop=Assistant.Method|planPitstop|false|true|1|Ask the Engineer to plan a pitstop.
simulatePitstop=Assistant.Method|recommendPitstop|false|true|1|Simulates the outcome of an upcoming pitstop. The traffic situation after the pitstop will be evaluated and the target lap will be optimized, if an undercut is possible.
updateStrategy=Assistant.Method|recommendStrategy|true|true|0|Trigger a recalculation of the current race strategy.
[Parameters]
planPitstop.1=targetLap|Integer||false|The planned lap for the car to come to the pit.
simulatePitstop.1=targetLap|Integer||false|The planned lap for the car to come to the pit.